<h1>Official ntfy.sh Debian repository</h1>

<p>This is the official Debian/Ubuntu package repository for <a href="https://ntfy.sh">ntfy</a>.</p>

<h2>Install instructions</h2>
<p>To allow the system to check the packages authenticity, you need to install the ntfy keyring:</p>
<pre>sudo mkdir -p /etc/apt/keyrings
sudo curl -L -o /etc/apt/keyrings/ntfy-keyring.gpg https://{{ repo_server_name }}/apt/keyring.gpg</pre>

<p>Then add the repository to your apt sources:</p>
<pre><code>echo "deb [signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/ntfy-keyring.gpg] https://{{ repo_server_name }}/apt stable main" \
  | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/ntfy.list
</code></pre>

<p>Finally, update and install:</p>
<pre><code>sudo apt update
sudo apt install ntfy
</code></pre>

<h2>Source</h2>
<p>Packages are built from the official <a href="https://github.com/binwiederhier/ntfy">ntfy GitHub repository</a>.</p>
